Privacy Policy

2. How We Use your Data
We use this data to: Authenticate users and provide access to CMDR. Monitor usage patterns and improve our services Comply with legal obligations.

Log Data may include information such as your computer's Internet Protocol (IP) address, browser type, machine model, activity you engage in on our pages, the referring URL, and access times and dates.
